Hey BDAA!
If you're interested in participating in an exclusive Pre-Event Networking Session with Bank of America tomorrow, please fill out the form below. This is a great opportunity to connect with industry professionals in a small group setting, share your resume, and ask questions.
Spots are limited! Only the first 30 people to RSVP will receive the exact time and location. This is a first-come, first-served opportunity:
https://forms.gle/FpVTz3fYWQ5XZb6z5
